A vintage 1950s-style office scene with a retro computer terminal displaying a glowing holiday wreath on its green monochrome screen, surrounded by scattered punch cards and manila folders on a mahogany desk. Through a frosted window, snow falls gently. A suspicious-looking envelope sits unopened beside the keyboard, casting an ominous shadow. The warm amber glow of a desk lamp contrasts with the cold blue winter light from outside, creating a mood of cautious curiosity. Muted color palette with pops of festive red and green reflected in the screen's glow.
